description.p: Five or More is the GNOME port of a once-popular computer game. Align five or more objects of the same color into a line to cause them to disappear and score points. Earn many more points by lining up as many objects as possible before clearing them.
More objects appear after every turn. Play for as long as possible, until the board is completely full!
